getEncoding(String) - Static method in class EncodingUtil
The method has one String parameter representing a 5-digit zip code and returns the complete bar encoding for the zip code, which is the concatenation of a full bar ("|"), the encoding of the five digits of the zip code, the encoding of the checksum digit, and a full bar ("|").

zipEncoding(String) - Static method in class EncodingUtil
